{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"清江（外一首）","authors":["喻晓"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":12,"day":2}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"清江（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喻晓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清江是神鸟的一支蓝羽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶摇上青云，向远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋树斑斓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘉桔芬芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸奇峰舒展笑颜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花像一群群白鸽飞翔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一川流动的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条美丽的画廊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舸翔舟飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腾起多少诱惑和梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江水给我一双透明的瞳孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到了一个伟大的希望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一江青春血液"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要三次发热发光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽起清流八百里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗我巴山贫困与苍凉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再用明珠万斛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我土家缀新装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清江是神鸟的一支蓝羽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶摇上青云，向远方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼峡口夜歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临水而美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸边泊一片苍茏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暮色中拾级而上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香炉石下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有座被发掘的夷城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破碎的瓦片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正复活悠远的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰腴的山腰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岩壁举着镇子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋顶上飘满绿色旗帜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜色被点燃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯光从云缝里轻轻逸出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插云而立的山峰如女神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江水是乌黑的长发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山月朦胧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复述廪君凄美了千年的爱情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此时苞谷烧酒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斟满了主人的盛情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们的脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漾出浓艳的秋色"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}